Articles.Content: Hi I'm new to ksp I've tried to install saturnv but I can't can I please have help

What do you mean? Can you please specify? Are craft files not working or you don't have the parts? It may be you don’t have the Making History DLC, which gives you 5-meter parts, F-1 engines, and more. And you mentioned you’re new to KSP. Start with goals like getting to orbit before you build a moon rocket.
ive got the dlc but what i want is the photo realistic

Are you trying to build it [from scratch/on your own in the VAB] or are you trying to download something and use it?
